snippet: Dozens of New York City Council employees write an open letter demanding sweeping changes that better protect their well-being and safety.
lead_paragraph: They say they have been habitually mistreated and intimidated, and have few meaningful ways to make their complaints heard without fear of reprisal.

snippet: Leon Cooperman, the billionaire former hedge fund manager, has taken umbrage at Ms. Warren and her platform.
lead_paragraph: Escalating the war of words between Wall Street and Senator Elizabeth Warren, Leon Cooperman, a billionaire money manager, denounced her recent tweet encouraging him to “pitch in a bit more” because of his success in life, saying she sounded like “a parent chiding an ungrateful child.”
